  <div class="pane-content">
    <h1 class="dedicated"><span style="color: #424242;">We are Dedicated to Professional Canadian</span> Playwrights and Plays</h1>
<p>Playwrights Guild of Canada champions the role of the playwright in the creation of vibrant Canadian theatre.</p>
<p style="color: #009cdb;"><strong>Advocating, Supporting, Promoting since 1972</strong></p>
<p class="dedicated-spacer">&nbsp;</p>
<div class="block-button"><a href="/plays">Purchase a Play</a></div>
