      <div class="inside"><div class="panels_pane panel-pane pane-custom pane-6" >
  
      <h2 class="pane-title">About PGC</h2>
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <p>PGC was established in 1972 as the Playwrights Co-op. The main purpose was to publish and distribute scripts to encourage more productions of Canadian plays. Since then, it has grown and now provides programs and services for over 500 members.</p>
<h1><a href="/about" style="color:#c8c8c8; text-decoration: none;">Mission.Vision.Values</a></h1>
<h1><a href="/membership" style="color:#c8c8c8; text-decoration: none;">Membership Info</a></h1>
<h1><a href="/about/programs-and-services" style="color:#c8c8c8; text-decoration: none;">Programs &amp; Services</a></h1>
  </div>

  
  </div>
</div>
    </div>

