  <div class="pane-content">
    <p>For all inquiries regarding the availability/ purchase of Copyscripts and Amateur Performing Rights please email: <a href="mailto:orders@playwrightsguild.ca" style="color: white;">orders@playwrightsguild.ca</a></p>
<h5>Mailing Address</h5>
<p>401 Richmond St. W<br />Suite #350<br />Toronto, Ontario<br />Canada, M5V 3A8</p>
<h5>Phone Numbers</h5>
<p>telephone: 416.703.0201<br />fax: 416.703.0059</p>
<h5>E-mail</h5>
<p>General Inquiries: <a href="mailto:info@playwrightsguild.ca" style="color: white;">info@playwrightsguild.ca</a></p>
